{"tid":1465190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警點解贏啊？因為佢地真係不篤灰、不割席、不分化啊！","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T17:56:02.000Z","uid":215648,"like":116,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f06c2c2e5ec0e5edad4004349b6b84d806b3c8","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"黑警點解贏啊？因為佢地真係不篤灰、不割席、不分化啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮示威者跑番狗總穿 - 扮無野<br />\n公安扮香港警察 - 不篤灰<br />\n打爆示威者既眼 - 不割席<br />\n<br />\n人地做到，點解我地做唔到啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n檢討策略：可以！<br />\n割？不了！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8d754c462fc20bc990058857df66cdc85e64b30b","tid":1465190,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287cd37cb2a749ddd4a9074e3ba2eb8c3375e4ca","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:35.000Z","msg":"自推一"},{"pid":"d43438d816a70977f8e64589b53b978cf85e117a","tid":1465190,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"813機場出真槍"},{"pid":"9708e24bc793f96b66bd9b26e76c07c49ef93ba3","tid":1465190,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"機場一役喺要喺「公安」同「醫護第一」之間取決一方，從而比對家分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對中共黎講犧牲一個公安<br />\n同收買一個金毛MK仔同收買啲人扮勇武掉野去警車唔係無可能<br />\n搵幾個人就挑起到你地內鬥<br />\n圍左公安咁耐有無得著？對五大訴求有無幫助？<br />\n唔喺幫個公安講說話，而喺處事要為大局著想<br />\n圍左三、四個鐘頭先上到醫護車<br />\n之後個金毛MK仔即刻第一時間沖出馬路靜坐阻路<br />\n我就覺得成年事好鬼鬼<br />\n根本喺一場中共/黑警Show<br />\n最大敵人根本就係你地自己<br />\n要時刻都有批判性思考<br />\n入得機場和理非就和理非<br />\n比中共睇穿你班人「好憎公安」同「讓路比醫護」兩者之間做出決定<br />\n萬死個公安死左就有位比人入<br />\n但就係咁比人分化你話抵唔抵？"},{"pid":"df14f74c75f2fce08a6afb19f152cd5fadbbfaea","tid":1465190,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"不篤灰、不割席、不分化"},{"pid":"16866e190b60cc24f2cb881578cfb23ba90dafbe","tid":1465190,"uid":65300,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"係因為佢地有槍  有武力  隻手遮天<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為佢地團結   係因為佢地想殺人<br />\n打人 開槍  非禮 老強  做咩都無罪 重有糧出   邊有咁好既工"},{"pid":"636480190c28be637799ce6701c069e9a33e8c69","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"自推二"},{"pid":"5ef656de9e65cb772f42c7242378a0ea8967d82a","tid":1465190,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"不割"},{"pid":"6992ee5aabe43ffb03b3497bcba740300f39f2d0","tid":1465190,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff4a642a85fef484b029f4730b1d06ddc8354fa7","tid":1465190,"uid":25569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d43438d816a70977f8e64589b53b978cf85e117a","tid":1465190,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"813機場出真槍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"生命受到威脅可以拔"},{"pid":"dd47827b8957f7408146e739af79c4ecee198d70","tid":1465190,"uid":287064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"不割席！<br />\n今日係因為人數唔夠，先迫到手足以block閘同衝嘅手法去達成目標，抗爭者要做嘅唔係同佢地割席，而係設法增加返人數，唔洗block閘就達成目標<br />\n<br />\n點解唔夠人？搞太密喇，如果可以搞返疏啲，或者可以用壓倒性人數去獲勝<br />\n<br />\n今日嘅問題係出在人數度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c091dee9a4c6072f9d7aad15536b0a921f77d089","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"fd8bd0cfdd7bb83cb6bdcf412999c2ed927b37f3","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:50.000Z","msg":"612中計<br />\n621中計<br />\n71中計<br />\n721中計<br />\n81中計<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">計你老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0776355e4ca505c44f325a5e294935aefe9a4513","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a846619ca9f6144fdd14110b60f4b5176301930","tid":1465190,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d414192f422583ccbc990a98c3e8f03fe66337d","tid":1465190,"uid":145863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"P牌無quota開post，借貼<br />\n<br />\n813係好混亂既一日....<br />\n<br />\n1. 有手足block check-in 想快速地癱瘓機場 /令航班取消，<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時好多手足反對，因為令到旅客充滿怨氣 / 變相輸民意。</span><br />\n2. 經過最近黑警做鬼既情況愈黎愈過份同愈目中無人，有手足係機場捉到鬼後，花大量時間圍鬼，<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時好多手足反對，因為覺得錯左焦點，而且因爲鬼係捉不完。</span><br />\n3. 有勇武派手足開始對機場內警犬進行比較激烈的反擊行為，反之然警方今次明顯表現比平常克制 （比較下顯得，並非真係克制），<span style=\"color: red;\">但同時有好多手足反對，因為係機場入面，係所有焦點，包括外國媒體下，係中了警方陷阱，係輸了形象和民意。</span><br />\n<br />\n所以所以，<br />\n係大家記得要團結，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割𥱊，不篤灰</span></span>的大前提下，813的混亂，大家屌過嬲過迷茫過後，<br />\n希望可以理性咁大家好好討論反個共識，<br />\n可以重新開始，進行止蝕工程。<br />\n要記得！<br />\n我地由69開始，去到今日不容易，<br />\n我地既付出，係唔會因爲一日既挫折就走向下波。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">煲底下的約定</span>，不要忘了。<br />\n屌完，豬隊友還是你最愛的香港手足。<br />\n邊撚個未豬過未7過？？<br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩大家重點諗諗：<br />\n1. 以後面對鬼的態度和做法。<br />\n2. 在機場內面對警犬的boundary。<br />\n3. 如何最有效影響機管局正常運作。<br />\n4. 如果重新重拾民意，表達對旅客歉意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油。<br />\n我愛你們。</span></span>"},{"pid":"a1dce7b13b81a438badcd40e31ef5c67b7a055d2","tid":1465190,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"不割！"},{"pid":"a376aa67992710c663fc685698c1eac0633d7a80","tid":1465190,"uid":108860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mqpqv0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqpqv0L.jpg&h=742d781b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n要割的話就諗番係咩驅使我地可以走到咁耐<br />\n<br />\n我地堅守住呢個信念，勇武和理非互相backup先可以有能力同政府鬥，無左呢個信念成個運動就會瓦解，2個月以來既努力就白廢，一失敗所以人都會被政府清算。社會信用，送中條例，教育營就會係失敗既後果。"},{"pid":"fe36638aefaf08e272c4e9842f1edb6cd9aa3365","tid":1465190,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:38.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 不讉責 不篤灰 不分化 不放棄"},{"pid":"4672e3726cdfd2a3dc52ccc5b1fc33f5bfcb9c1b","tid":1465190,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf9419a0e79ff16bf88da58dbd93463d7a6551d","tid":1465190,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"746527974d462858d2e2a9fa523929c6e43b7eb9","tid":1465190,"uid":189214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45d96eb93ae4e99ff0d3bf7c29bf916f32d37f8d","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4afe5995ce8733b857d3701f987137a6c55763","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a1f893eba92e603e7b41043ecfad6c088e2cda","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e89c87e5075e2dbc5db3309856eed1e99c704b","tid":1465190,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"da275254f6924cd5d892bad046c1f0a0ab45b719","tid":1465190,"uid":12426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"和理非請用和理非手法   就算有鬼在場   和理非會贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467533\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467533</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fc0cbf69658d9977e4a6b978b08fb53cbda87593","tid":1465190,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:14.000Z","msg":"因為你冇機會放鬼去警察度<br />\n因為你冇用假料老屈佢<br />\n人地一路用緊錢去維繫大家"},{"pid":"2c643cf46788b66a11f42fd38a7ac1b55ede44ad","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ec9934adfa6e34f1c50469abd565ee2ccfd2cc","tid":1465190,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e00e489fa5b6e7873993a2ba2338284d2cba8f3","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aa8db28344924e6817d552b6af39eb9b17c511","tid":1465190,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcd116ab23b3afbbe261e7da3e7b205a810e116","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80962f5670c3cb36f4b5d327fff0aeca9cb1448e","tid":1465190,"uid":72447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:29:52.000Z","msg":"佢哋做咩都無後果駛咩諗咁多？一齊踩曱甴幾咁愉快。<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔同，我哋如果唔齊上齊落，後果就係一路消耗，拉吓一個走吓兩個。<br />\n<br />\n大家應該都感覺到今次手足之間嘅信任有幾傷。<br />\n<br />\n中場休息，沉著應戰。"},{"pid":"be09efe3c24a75ec359895605b30c20077b84f94","tid":1465190,"uid":99787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:44:38.000Z","msg":"你地班民意撚 為左區區幾個外國遊客 <br />\n而去指責班手足 咁易被人分化 <br />\n對唔對得住比人拉左既手足 已死既義士呀！<br />\n而家個女仔冇左隻眼呀！一世嫁！<br />\n搵一次團結下好唔好呀 唔好再重演雨傘啦！"},{"pid":"b8f6a5259dee5510f6140a6ff7a3a4c98c2c5df1","tid":1465190,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLDhR3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLDhR3q.png&h=3bca9f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0095beee770e2b62e419b01768b969e585e91d","tid":1465190,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:54:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n813 之事其實情有可原，因為比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲，我地大家絕對唔會割蓆，但我地亦都要持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩提議大家投票決定，呢個亦係民主真諦，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所有社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，呢個係好自然亦好常見嘅事，可貴之處就係識得自省，至少我覺得813 呢一日明顯唔係end game 嘅一日，如果有朝一日真係end game 嘅係一戰竟全功嘅時候咁到時我地做乜嘢都可以，但喺呢一日來臨之前嘅過程上，我地唔可以急，仇恨係要記住因為係一股推動力，但亦要避免比仇恨支配行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">古今歷史上每一場運動係需要好長時日去完成，而且過程係一定會出現爭拗，除咗不割蓆不分化，自省改進，檢討得失，去改善下一步行動亦係成功之道。</span><br />\n<br />\n已經發生咗嘅事我地冇辦法再去改變，比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲所以我地亦冇資格去怪責甚至割蓆，但我好希望呢場運動可以成功，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要反省，反省完就要檢討，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏，如果出現失誤唔去檢討，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。<br />\n<br />\n完美係一種永遠唔會達到但可以追求嘅哲學，所以我地只有不斷改善自己，互相指正，幫大家補鑊，一齊進步，一齊向成功之日進發，煲底之日我地仲要一齊慶祝"},{"pid":"e4e381122841680e127341b0a4fe1a17b2d59584","tid":1465190,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:55:35.000Z","msg":"挺"},{"pid":"dc5c819a7763f9b80c0255b661731458a526f83d","tid":1465190,"uid":272471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f06c2c2e5ec0e5edad4004349b6b84d806b3c8","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"黑警點解贏啊？因為佢地真係不篤灰、不割席、不分化啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮示威者跑番狗總穿 - 扮無野<br />\n公安扮香港警察 - 不篤灰<br />\n打爆示威者既眼 - 不割席<br />\n<br />\n人地做到，點解我地做唔到啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n檢討策略：可以！<br />\n割？不了！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:19.000Z","msg":"警察贏係因為佢哋思想扭曲同有錢收<br />\n我哋做唔到係因為我哋有良心<br />\n我哋做唔到係因為我哋尊重其他人<br />\n我哋做唔到係因為我哋接納其他人嘅意見！"},{"pid":"b4716f18806f675e7d39f5ebbef5374f94ffc2c9","tid":1465190,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:04:25.000Z","msg":"班黑警有贏過咩？<br />\n明明有頭比人屌到落尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲係做到不割蓆不分化，同埋盲撐<br />\n所以咪一直活係自己世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，但要檢討"},{"pid":"9ef581b9b0a3ea1bb2e72af30d285b889eaa894a","tid":1465190,"uid":267822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思阻一阻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請文宣組做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nspin返件事去721<br />\n<br />\n<strong>813 <br />\n警察和速龍遠道機場拯救假扮示威者的公安<br />\n721<br />\n警察也不到元朗救被白衣人恐襲的香港市民</strong>"},{"pid":"0efdec5d99d8ec742efa72eff9477a8316197e2e","tid":1465190,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:11:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"13655d73b5224c455ef3b5921c013b76b968a23f","tid":1465190,"uid":289590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"黑警同藍絲都唔識獨立思考，所以呢個榜樣我唔會理"},{"pid":"6e363b73dd4f523adce0e3a08d13801ed61bb945","tid":1465190,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3ab7e68cabc3c7c92b7ae33a279123d8c3f733","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"不要說： 做錯了<br />\n說：不完美，但可以接受。"},{"pid":"a0f4bce740f524e2dbf66df3ab691edbc451aa65","tid":1465190,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50390fa389eadd6db762cd7ec061bdb787bcf07f","tid":1465190,"uid":215648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdcc39374be078578af0d4c5e0cca2fcc394f8c","tid":1465190,"uid":79910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"自己人做咩都讚 做得好"},{"pid":"2625c9267686b1b4e9e8f7c4829f24925d2306dd","tid":1465190,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}